WEBVTT

00:06:57.502 --> 00:07:00.449
Meaning can be quiet

00:07:00.449 --> 00:07:02.620
and introverted.

00:07:02.620 --> 00:07:08.548
Maybe we make one small decision about our lives

00:07:08.548 --> 00:07:13.626
that can bring about big change.

00:07:13.626 --> 00:07:15.566
Many years ago, I had a patient,

00:07:15.566 --> 00:07:17.571
just a wonderful young man

00:07:17.571 --> 00:07:20.306
who was loved by the staff,

00:07:20.306 --> 00:07:23.190
and so it was something of a shock to us to realize

00:07:23.190 --> 00:07:26.974
that he had no friends.

00:07:26.974 --> 00:07:29.280
He lived by himself,

00:07:29.280 --> 00:07:33.308
he would come in for chemotherapy by himself,